<p>As you can see I would execute the <code>.height()</code> function many times to check for my conditions. Very unnecessary practice soon I came to find out.</p>

<p>Two weeks into bootcamp and I was taught how to keep it 'DRY' (Don't Repeat Yourself). (See example below).</p>

